*Nikad* nisam videla taj grad. (I have never seen that city.)
Niko *nikad* nije došao na njen rođendan. (Nobody has ever come to her birthday.)
*Nikad* nismo uspeli da obavimo tu misiju. (We have never succeeded in completing that mission.)
On nije *nikad* putovao u inostranstvo. (He has never traveled abroad.)
Ona *nikad* nije živela u tom gradu. (She has never lived in that city.)